			title: "In machiyotl",
			txt: "<p>Mochintin itocahuan ihuan itlamanitiliz in picietl ica iteohuelitiliz ihuan ohuicayo ihuelitiliz quitlalia cualli tlamanpan. In mexica quipiya in picietl huel iuhqui in tlamantli in momoztla tlamantli ihuan in teomahuiztic tlamantli. Cohualo in tenexyetl ipan tianquiztli ipampa cualli in momoztla tlamantli nozo mocuitlalpiya in teuctli, in mimatini ticitl ihuan in temixihuitiani nozo tlateomahuiztililizco ipan in teocalli \"itic amo hueyi ayotli motlali in xochitl ica mochi in picietl occe ica in contlilli, in ayotli itoca iyetecon\", oquito fray Diego Duran. Nozo tlamanalo in xinachtli ipan Coatepetl, oquito in tlaca in tlatataca ipampa tlamati. Tleco in picietl ompa ilhuicatlitic inic in tlanenehulia in Toci ihuan  in Cihuacoatl. </p><p>Ipampa ixochime in picietl, ca yehuatl ipan in itlacuicuiliz in Xochipilli ica mochintin cualli tlamantli, iteotlaman ihuan intlaixpanyouh in mexica. In \"ontequixtiliztli\" in yehuatl  huel oquito in moyolcocolti in Sahagun azo in quicentetilia icualtlaman in xihuitl. Ca in yehuantin in xochime, in icualtiliz in \"huey tlamacehualiztli\" ihuan \"in teyollaliliztli\". Yehuantin quinotza in yoliliztli. Oquito Sahagun, xoxoctic ihuan coztic in yiexochitl catca \"in quetzalizquixochitl, in cacahuaxochitl\" macalo in Huitzilopochtli ipan imachiyouh in ihuitl, ce tecpatl. Inin catca in nececeltiliztli axcan in teomahuiztic. Oquito Sahagun ipan itlateomauiztililiz in Xilonen, in itoca Huey Tecuilhuitl, yancuican in xihuitl huel quinnecui in picietl ihuan in cempohualxochitl. Ca in iahuiyayaliz in xochitl in tlatlilanilli itechpa tlatoa in atoctli ihuan in yoliliztli. </p><p>Tel tlamanalo in xochime no cualo inic teteo. Cepan in yehuantin in imachiyouh in cuicatl ica papaquiliztli, necuiltonoliztli ihuan ahahuializtli. Yehuatin tlacati ipan teomahuizticayotl. \"Cualli ye xochitl / ye ce tonequimilol / [...] ca tictotlanehuiya / in tlalticpaca [...] xochitl ya oquihuinti ye noyollo / quetzalyexochitl cuepontimania/ imapan ye nonnemi / nonxochinahuala\" (Romances de los Señores de la Nueva España). </p><p>Cece piloalo in xochitl ipan Xochipilli in teittitia mochitin tlamantli in tlacatiya in ce teotl ica in imachiyouh in tlalli  no in imachiyouh teomahuizticayotl. Axcan popotzalo in picietl ipan tlateomatiliztli in quiahuilt tla ca in tlatlaniliztli nozo in netlazocamatiliztli ihuan ompa in nemi in tlaca in tlalitic Mexico.</p><p>Axcan quinequia in quimati \"in temaxaloque in xochime\" in picietl, no quinequi inin xoxochitla ihuan ipan in milli ipampa icualtiliz, iahuiyayaliz in xochime.</p>",
