			txt: "<p>Momatia in macpalxochitl in cuauhtla ica miec mixitl ihuan occe cuauhtla in Mexico nozo ipan Guatemala. Momatia in tlatotoyan huel tlacpac, 2500 metros icpac huye atl.</p><p>Teittia in macuilli in xochizhuatl huel iniuhqui temapil in tlaixiptlatia ce matl ica imapil in tlapouhqui, ihuan \"quipiya itic in tlapalli in chichiltic ihuan in coztic ihuan occe chichiltic ipani\", oquito Francisco Hernandez. Cuepinia in pehua in primavera ixquichca verano. Zan occenca amo oquittaque in macpalxochitl in Mexico ipampa momatia huel tlacpac ihuan amo huel quitoca occe in tlalli. No zan occenca quinequi in tlaca quitoca in xochitl tel amo hueliti. Teittia in xochitl in cualli occe altepetl in America. Zan quin ceppa quitoca in macpalxochitl itic ical virrey in Mexico ixquichca siglo XIX.</p><p>Zan ce oquito fray Bernardino de Sahagun ipan in huey amoxtli. Itic \"in xochitla ihuan ca in yehuatl in cuahuitl\", teittitia in macpalxochitl. \"ca in yehuatl in xochime itoca macpalxochitl in xochitla huel iniuhqui imapil in tema. Azo teittia in cualli xochitla quipiya in tlatoani. Inin teittia quitlazotla in xochitl ihuan in yollocayotl in tlaca in quitoca in xochitl, \"in iamantecauh in xochime\".</p><p>Azo oquito Hernandez amo quimati in quipatia in xochitl. Azo ayac quimati in quipati inin ipampa camo in Mexico, no amo huel quitoca. Azo in zan tlacatl amo mochtin quipiya in quipatia.</p><p>Oquito Martin de la Cruz, ipan Codice De la Cruz-Badiano tla quintesi in cuauhehuatl ihuan in xochizhuatl \"quipatiz in tepilli nozo in tepolli\" ca yehuatl in cuitlatitiquiliztli nozo in pozahuacayotl.</p><p>Axcan quipatia ica macpalxochitl. Quipatia in ixcocoliztli in teyollo, in huihuixca. In ixochihuan in teacotlaza ihuan quipatli in eztli iyohui ihuan quipatia in ixcocoliztli huel iniuqui aca in tlahuanqui. In tlacatl in quimati, inin xochitl amo huel quimati.</p><p>Axcan occe altepetl ixochizhuahuan iuh tlamani quitlapachoa in tamalli inic in tlateomatiliztli.</p>",
